    <!--
    ===========================================
    HOW TO ADD A NEW RELEASE:
    ===========================================

    1. Build your .dmg file
    2. Sign it with: ./sign_update YourApp.dmg
    3. Get the file size: ls -l YourApp.dmg
    4. Copy the <item> template below and fill in:
       - sparkle:version (build number, e.g., 2)
       - sparkle:shortVersionString (version, e.g., 1.0.1)
       - pubDate (RFC 2822 format)
       - url (download URL)
       - sparkle:edSignature (from sign_update output)
       - length (file size in bytes)
    5. Add release notes in <description>

    ===========================================
    -->

    <item>
